Frist you have to bring Pizza base from shop
then you have to cut the vegetables you wanted ex(capsicum,onion,tomato etc)
then you have to fry the vegetabes in heated oil (about 50%) Add red chilli flakes,Oregano and chinese salt

Take Pizza base and apply Pizza Pasta sos on it 
now put the vegetables on it and spread vegetabes on the base
and put cheese on it 

now take one plate and put in the oven 
for 20 minutes (i dont know the tempture)
and it is ready for EAT